705684f-a.title: Brooklyn: Meeker Avenue - Stewart Street
705684f-a.text:
Meeker Avenue, east of Stewart Street, showing in the back-
ground the Meeker Avenue Bridge. At the leNh is J.G. Leary Iumber
Co. yard.
Augmst 13, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
